1
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:52,520
I heard that recently,

2
00:00:52,520 --> 00:00:54,680
you've been getting close to Miss Qiu.

3
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:56,520
We were classmates when studying abroad,

4
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:58,040
so we're somewhat friendly.

5
00:00:58,040 --> 00:00:58,600
Good.

6
00:01:00,120 --> 00:01:02,200
It seems your taste in a future wife

7
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:03,570
is actually quite good.

8
00:01:03,880 --> 00:01:06,520
If our Ji family can ally with the Qiu family,

9
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:10,210
we might even be able to enter politics in the future.

10
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:12,000
Dad, we aren't...

11
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:13,160
Master.

12
00:01:13,520 --> 00:01:15,520
Someone delivered a crate outside.

13
00:01:17,039 --> 00:01:17,760
What crate?

14
00:01:18,320 --> 00:01:19,880
It's a crate from our Chamber of Commerce.

15
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:20,740
How about this?

16
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:21,980
I'll go take a look.

17
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:22,920
Go take a look.

18
00:01:22,960 --> 00:01:23,420
Please.

19
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:26,440
Young Master.

20
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:27,240
It's this box.

21
00:01:27,240 --> 00:01:28,000
Quan

22
00:01:28,039 --> 00:01:28,320
Quan

23
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:30,840
Long.

24
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:31,039
Jin

25
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:31,440
Shou.

26
00:01:31,440 --> 00:01:33,039
What kind of goods are these?

27
00:01:36,039 --> 00:01:37,320
Bing-6 South-2.

28
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:39,120
2673.

29
00:01:40,039 --> 00:01:41,700
Shengde House raw materials.

30
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:42,700
Furong Street.

31
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:46,009
It's the goods for Zheng's Match Factory.

32
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:48,200
It should be saltpeter inside.

33
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:49,160
Saltpeter.

34
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:51,490
When was it shipped?

35
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,880
The 8th of this month.

36
00:01:53,440 --> 00:01:56,080
It arrived at the Zheng Residence three days ago.

37
00:01:56,080 --> 00:01:57,740
Then why was it sent back here?

38
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:58,650
I don't know.

39
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:00,960
Two people from the police station came.

40
00:02:00,960 --> 00:02:02,160
They dropped it off and left.

41
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:03,290
The police station?

42
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:04,000
Open it up.

43
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:13,920
I'm suffocating.

44
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:14,560
It's you.

45
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:16,120
Are you interested

46
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:18,760
in watching me channel spirits?

47
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:20,600
Chief,

48
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:22,100
we found a new suspect.

49
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:25,160
Wu Yue suspects it's the Zheng family's concubine, Ma Yanmei.

50
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:26,620
She planned this revenge.

51
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,640
Man Dali was just framed.

52
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:29,840
Ma Yanmei?

53
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:33,420
How come I don't know about such a person?

54
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,240
Besides,

55
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:36,240
the words of a little spirit medium...

56
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,560
do you actually believe them?

57
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:39,160
We don't believe the spirit medium,

58
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:40,160
but the evidence.

59
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:42,400
Now all the evidence points to this person.

60
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:45,240
Since when is it your turn to teach me how to do my job?

61
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:47,640
If I say someone is guilty, they are guilty.

62
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:49,400
I found it.

63
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:54,280
Who let you in?

64
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:56,340
Making such a racket here.

65
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:58,820
Chief Song, I'm here to report a case.

66
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:00,570
Young Master Ji,

67
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:01,800
what kind of case are you reporting?

68
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:03,440
According to the porters at my Chamber of Commerce,

69
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:04,040
three days ago,

70
00:03:04,040 --> 00:03:06,200
they delivered a box of saltpeter to the Zheng Residence.

71
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:06,800
But later,

72
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:08,200
this box appeared again

73
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:10,260
in the alley near the General Temple.

74
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:12,800
What kind of mess is this?

75
00:03:12,920 --> 00:03:13,400
This...

76
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:16,560
Ma Yanmei used this box

77
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:18,240
to hold Zheng Jinxian's body

78
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:20,040
and transport it to Jiangjun Temple in advance.

79
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:22,720
Zheng Jinxian's death has nothing to do with Man Dali.

80
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:25,650
It was Ma Yanmei and Gu Mancang who conspired to do it.

81
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:26,560
Wait.

82
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,840
And I've detected

83
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:30,240
traces of Zheng Jinxian on the wooden planks of the box.

84
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:32,570
The one you should arrest now is Ma Yanmei.

85
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,560
Chief.

86
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:34,840
What is it now?

87
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,240
Chief.

88
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:39,120
Outside,

89
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,880
there's a crowd surrounding us.

90
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:42,280
They are all protesting.

91
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:44,920
Free Man Dali!

92
00:03:45,079 --> 00:03:46,440
Man Dali is innocent!

93
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,920
Man Dali is innocent!

94
00:03:48,160 --> 00:03:49,840
The police are framing Man Dali!

95
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,640
The police are framing Man Dali!

96
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:52,720
Free Man Dali!

97
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:54,160
Man Dali is innocent!

98
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,680
Man Dali is innocent!

99
00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:57,480
The police are framing Man Dali!

100
00:03:57,480 --> 00:03:59,200
Man Dali is innocent! Quiet!

101
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:01,560
Quiet down!

102
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:03,560
Everyone,

103
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:04,960
please calm down.

104
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:08,480
We'll release Man Dali once we find the truth.

105
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:12,560
We'll give you a satisfactory answer.

106
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:15,460
Why isn't she here yet?

107
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:20,130
Let's go.

108
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:22,130
Qiu Ya is waiting for us over there.

109
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:28,700
Mrs. Zheng.

110
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,440
You are such a philanthropist.

111
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:31,960
You actually sold off the Zheng family's assets

112
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:33,220
to fund the orphanage.

113
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:34,780
What was your motivation?

114
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:39,000
I am just a woman.

115
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,960
I don't know much about that.

116
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:42,880
I just wanted to do some good.

117
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,400
If I may ask,

118
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:47,120
your husband passed away recently.

119
00:04:47,200 --> 00:04:48,800
You neither claimed his body

120
00:04:49,200 --> 00:04:50,960
nor arranged his funeral.

121
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,760
My husband died long ago.

122
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:57,280
He died a year ago.

123
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,370
So, did you do all of this

124
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,840
to avenge him?

125
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:02,440
Mr. Qiu,

126
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,490
what do you mean by that?

127
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:07,880
Ma Yanmei.

128
00:05:08,640 --> 00:05:10,840
The last channeling for Chen Afeng failed.

129
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:12,280
Let me channel for you again.

130
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:13,010
How about it?

131
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:19,920
All right.

132
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,460
I'd love nothing more.

133
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,120
Ma Yanmei,

134
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:35,980
I'm going to start.

135
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,360
Can I really

136
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:40,280
speak to him again?

137
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:42,080
Yes.

138
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:44,490
But you must tell the truth.

139
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:46,720
You can hide things from the living,

140
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,980
but you can't hide them

141
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:50,080
from the dead.

142
00:05:58,480 --> 00:06:00,960
Close the Yang Gate, open the Yin Gate.

143
00:06:01,080 --> 00:06:03,760
Wandering spirits, stay away.

144
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:06,720
Open the path to the Underworld.

145
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:11,480
Feng.

146
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,040
Feng.

147
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:14,850
The water turns bloody.

148
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:17,040
The sins in this room

149
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,520
must be revealed.

150
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:22,120
One step, two steps.

151
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:24,730
Three Yin, Four Yang, open the ghost's mouth.

152
00:06:25,080 --> 00:06:26,680
Chen Afeng, oh, Chen Afeng.

153
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:28,280
You died unjustly.

154
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:30,840
Identify your killer today.

155
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:33,420
Gather the karma of the mortal world.

156
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:36,480
Dissolve the sins of this life now.

157
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,480
Xiaomei.

158
00:06:41,080 --> 00:06:41,840
Xiaomei.

159
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,400
I died a miserable death.

160
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:45,440
Feng.

161
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:47,159
I know you died unjustly.

162
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:49,080
Do you know how I died?

163
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:51,480
It was Gu Mancang.

164
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:54,120
A year ago,

165
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,360
I was still mourning you.

166
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:59,080
The neighbors kept bullying me.

167
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:02,320
So I went to the Zheng household as a maid

168
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:03,960
to seek refuge.

169
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,880
You didn't give anything away, did you?

170
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:06,440
No.

171
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:09,420
It was staged as an accidental phosphorus fire.

172
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:12,080
The family paid fifty silver dollars to settle it.

173
00:07:12,080 --> 00:07:13,840
Not only did the police find nothing,

174
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:16,160
but their family was even grateful to us.

175
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:18,040
Just like Chen Afeng.

176
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:22,440
I know I can count on you.

177
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:24,930
Who is it?

178
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:32,120
What are you doing here?

179
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,640
I was discussing important matters with the Master.

180
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:35,800
You didn't hear anything you shouldn't have, did you?

181
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,920
I just got here

182
00:07:37,159 --> 00:07:38,800
and slipped.

183
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,810
I didn't hear anything.

184
00:07:40,840 --> 00:07:41,640
Xiaomei,

185
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:43,000
you married into the Zheng family

186
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,720
to avenge me, right?

187
00:07:45,159 --> 00:07:46,080
Yes.

188
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:47,800
Get up, quick.

189
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,720
Are you hurt?

190
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,170
Let me rub it for you.

191
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:53,080
Butler Gu,

192
00:07:53,960 --> 00:07:56,820
I'll go fetch fresh water for the Master right away.

193
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:58,000
Wait.

194
00:07:58,760 --> 00:07:59,760
Come in first.

195
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:01,560
Serve me while I have a smoke.

196
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:05,440
That night, I seduced Zheng Jinxian

197
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:07,060
and became his concubine.

198
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:08,210
Coming, Master.

199
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:11,690
It was all to find evidence to expose them.

200
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,260
Gu Mancang and Zheng Jinxian,

201
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:18,440
they deserve a horrible death.

202
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:26,640
Even a chicken I raise knows how to lay eggs.

203
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:27,920
You useless waste.

204
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:30,360
Why aren't you pregnant with my seed yet?

205
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:32,690
I'll beat you to death, you useless thing.

206
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:36,419
I didn't expect

207
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:38,360
Gu Mancang

208
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:42,200
is actually Old Master Zheng's illegitimate son.

209
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:45,000
Their whole family are devils.

210
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:51,160
Master.

211
00:08:51,800 --> 00:08:54,400
I used to be in the human trafficking business.

212
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:56,840
Or I could buy a few sons for you.

213
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,240
Mancang.

214
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:01,520
Was your mother named Ping'er,

215
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:04,920
from the Sun family in Xiwang Village?

216
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:07,880
Master, how did you know?

217
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:12,520
When my father went to the countryside to collect rent,

218
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:14,120
he slept with your mother.

219
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:17,520
Later, to raise a bastard like you,

220
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:19,560
she started working in a brothel,

221
00:09:19,560 --> 00:09:20,400
didn't she?

222
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,160
Master, this...

223
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:23,960
Where did you hear such rumors?

224
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,440
I wouldn't dare claim ties to the Zheng family.

225
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:27,280
Don't play dumb with me.

226
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:29,060
I'm just asking you one thing.

227
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:31,600
Are you here for revenge,

228
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:34,680
or to get rich?

229
00:09:36,160 --> 00:09:36,800
Master,

230
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:38,880
I wouldn't dare have any ulterior motives.

231
00:09:38,880 --> 00:09:40,540
I can serve you for a lifetime.

232
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:42,000
As long as I'm fed and clothed,

233
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,280
I'll be satisfied.

234
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:47,720
Mancang.

235
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:50,400
With your nature,

236
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:53,200
you're nine parts dog.

237
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:55,280
And one part

238
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:59,600
human.

239
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,360
One part human is enough.

240
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:04,360
That is enough.

241
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:05,740
Thank you, Master.

242
00:10:05,800 --> 00:10:06,860
Thank you, Master.

243
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:10,920
If you can provide an heir for the Zheng family.

244
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:13,720
It's better than giving my estate

245
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:18,040
to a kidnapped bastard.

246
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:22,800
Master,

247
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,680
what do you mean?

248
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:27,680
You.

249
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:28,960
Do her.

250
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:31,160
This...

251
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,080
Master,

252
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:35,480
don't be kidding.

253
00:10:36,880 --> 00:10:38,440
Do her tonight.

254
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:42,200
When she bears a child who takes the Zheng name,

255
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:45,320
I can treat you as half family.

256
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:46,400
If you refuse,

257
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:48,740
pack your things and get the hell out.

258
00:10:49,400 --> 00:10:52,760
If you dare mention the name Zheng outside,

259
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:56,960
I'll have your tongue ripped out

260
00:10:57,760 --> 00:10:59,480
and your legs broken.

261
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:08,460
Thank you for the reward, Master.

262
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:10,040
No.

263
00:11:10,400 --> 00:11:10,880
Don't.

264
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:12,560
You beast!

265
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:14,000
Let go of me!

266
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:15,880
Later,

267
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:18,920
I kept instigating Gu Mancang

268
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:20,960
to kill Zheng Jinxian.

269
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:21,980
Light it up.

270
00:11:24,040 --> 00:11:24,600
Master,

271
00:11:25,280 --> 00:11:26,440
we're out of Fushou Paste.

272
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:28,400
Go buy some. Get it for me now!

273
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:29,680
Master! Master!

274
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:30,700
Master!

275
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:31,880
I have some here.

276
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:33,520
I've already prepared it for you.

277
00:11:33,520 --> 00:11:34,080
Light it.

278
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:34,960
Hurry.

279
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,050
That feels good.

280
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:47,880
Mancang,

281
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:50,320
you are closer to me than my own brother.

282
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:54,280
Since this 'brother' has slaved away for you,

283
00:11:54,560 --> 00:11:57,490
shouldn't the Zheng family assets be returned to me?

284
00:11:59,400 --> 00:12:01,280
You're dreaming.

285
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:04,760
You're just a dog I raised.

286
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:06,860
Do you really think you're human?

287
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:11,200
Then today, I won't be human.

288
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:15,440
Go to hell.

289
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:16,800
You pair of dogs!

290
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:18,320
Don't kill me! Once you're dead,

291
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,560
everything is mine.

292
00:12:23,800 --> 00:12:24,920
Old bastard.

293
00:12:41,880 --> 00:12:42,760
We did it.

294
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:47,180
Don't celebrate too soon.

295
00:12:47,680 --> 00:12:48,360
Next,

296
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:51,760
we need to pack Zheng Jinxian into a crate

297
00:12:52,560 --> 00:12:54,040
and take him to the General Temple.

298
00:12:54,040 --> 00:12:55,280
Why go through all that trouble?

299
00:12:55,280 --> 00:12:56,280
Just bury him right here.

300
00:12:56,280 --> 00:12:58,320
Zheng Jinxian can't just vanish.

301
00:12:58,680 --> 00:13:00,210
It would arouse suspicion.

302
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:03,080
You can't be the butler anymore.

303
00:13:03,880 --> 00:13:05,610
I'll replace all the servants.

304
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:07,060
From now on,

305
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:09,040
you are Master Zheng.

306
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:11,020
This old thing looks hideous.

307
00:13:11,560 --> 00:13:13,560
How will people believe I'm the one who died?

308
00:13:13,560 --> 00:13:14,760
That doesn't matter.

309
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,520
We'll use a trick.

310
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:19,130
As long as there are witnesses,

311
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:21,220
we'll say the corpse reanimated.

312
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:23,600
The police will just think it's bad luck.

313
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:26,060
They won't investigate closely.

314
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:30,640
You really are a great help to me.

315
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:32,120
When this is done,

316
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:33,970
I'll make you the main wife.

317
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:39,040
Then have him put on a fake mustache

318
00:13:39,920 --> 00:13:41,650
to impersonate Zheng Jinxian.

319
00:13:46,280 --> 00:13:47,010
Are you okay,

320
00:13:47,040 --> 00:13:47,640
Ma Yanmei?

321
00:13:49,680 --> 00:13:51,520
So you used arsenic to kill Gu Mancang too,

322
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:52,180
didn't you?

323
00:13:57,800 --> 00:14:00,000
He was insatiably greedy and heartless.

324
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,440
Didn't he deserve to die?

325
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:07,930
The police came to the house today.

326
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:08,800
What?

327
00:14:09,400 --> 00:14:10,460
What did they find?

328
00:14:10,880 --> 00:14:11,600
Nothing.

329
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:14,400
I heard the rickshaw puller was released,

330
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:16,380
and the case is closed.

331
00:14:16,680 --> 00:14:17,440
Tomorrow,

332
00:14:17,880 --> 00:14:20,410
you can return to the Zheng residence openly.

333
00:14:22,040 --> 00:14:22,920
Good.

334
00:14:23,640 --> 00:14:26,440
Yanmei's substitution trick was brilliant.

335
00:14:26,760 --> 00:14:28,480
The Zheng estate is ours now.

336
00:14:29,920 --> 00:14:31,450
Don't celebrate too early.

337
00:14:32,440 --> 00:14:33,100
From now on,

338
00:14:34,240 --> 00:14:37,880
you still have to wear a fake beard and pretend to be Zheng Jinxian.

339
00:14:37,880 --> 00:14:41,140
Wait until the managers at the match factory are replaced,

340
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:42,640
before you can go out.

341
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:43,880
Don't worry.

342
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:47,020
I handled all the out-of-town business.

343
00:14:47,040 --> 00:14:48,240
At worst, we'll leave Shencheng

344
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:49,800
and open a factory somewhere else.

345
00:14:49,800 --> 00:14:51,560
With the Zheng family's assets,

346
00:14:51,560 --> 00:14:53,620
we can live a carefree life anywhere.

347
00:14:57,960 --> 00:14:58,880
Xiangxiang.

348
00:15:13,920 --> 00:15:15,180
Why aren't you eating?

349
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:16,540
I ate before I came.

350
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:33,320
I've been suffocating these past two days.

351
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:35,680
Why don't we have some fun?

352
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:36,840
Come here.

353
00:15:37,560 --> 00:15:39,090
You really have some nerve.

354
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:41,060
In front of the General's statue,

355
00:15:42,920 --> 00:15:44,850
aren't you afraid of retribution?

356
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:47,920
Being poor for a lifetime is the real retribution.

357
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:57,840
It hurts.

358
00:15:58,480 --> 00:16:00,760
Here comes the karma.
